name: Fish Life.
description: Underwater is always fun, the cute playful Fish is very aggressive and starting its water life in breathtaking adventurous journey. Never let fish goes down which might take away its life, keep tap and drive this cute fish on its way without getting into the fishing nets which arranged in a tricky way and these looks colorful but harmful these nets will take away your fish life. There are many rings on its way you have to pass through them to grow your points without colliding its edges. There are crystal blocks hurdles be careful and pass through the gaps. Play this wonderful, colorful Fish Life game and share with your family and friends.
